      • ADD_DOMAIN_TC

        public void ADD_DOMAIN_TC()
        Summary
        Add Domain
        Pre-Conditions
        DashBoard page should be open
        User should have administrator rights
        Steps
        1. Click on Username on right upper corner of browser window.
        2. click on 'Domains'
        3. Click on 'Add Domain'
        4. Enter Domain name
        5. Click on 'Add'
        6. Share a file
        7. Enter email address which contains domain name added
        8. Click on 'Yes'
        9. Click on 'Close'
        Expected Result:
        1. Verify that alert stating that 'domain is restricted' should be present
